Ask pem243 about CentrePoint on Colombo Motel



This review is the subjective opinion of a TripAdvisor member and not of TripAdvisor LLC. 


Centrepoint1, Owner at CentrePoint on Colombo Motel, responded to this review,
March 24, 2012


Hello pem243 and thank you for the review. Once again, we are pleased to see such a seasoned Trip Advisor user satisfied with their stay with us. Glad you liked our style of service and our eco stance. And yes! while the laundry machine does its magic you can take a stroll to see the latest in Christchurch. After the quakes the cityscape is changing almost daily and we are happy to see things moving forward!



Report response as inappropriate

Thank you. We appreciate your input.


