Hello Stuartessaouira and thank you for the review. It is indeed an honour to get a review from a well travelled reviewer. We agree with you that we are a good motel close to town. We also agree that in some parts of town, there is not much left to see but in other parts there are things to see and we can give advice to our guests on the best places to go! Thanks for the review.



