Mr_RJ_and_Mrs_MMD_H



Wellington, New Zealand






1 review 





“Family Re-Union”


Reviewed March 14, 2012




Went to Christchurch for a family re-union & needed somewhere close to the city centre. CentrePoint on Columbo was perfectly located and reasonable well priced. The complementaries & eco-friendly way in which they are presented is a breath of fresh air in today's fast paced consumerist world. Providing a recycling basket & eco-friendly (the brand) shampoo, conditioner, handwash & dishwashing liquid was a step in the right direction espescially for staying in line with the Clean, Green New Zealand image.


Room Tip: All rooms are well sound-proofed & never heard a thing. Room 5 was a good 'Standard Studio...
See more room tips





Stayed March 2012, traveled as a couple



