Hello there Mr_RJ_and_Mrs_MMD_H and thanks for the review after visiting Christchurch for the family reunion. Glad that you liked our central city location and also found the price to your liking. AND thank you for taking the time tocomment in detail about our eco-friendly stance. We continue to do what we can. Glad that you liked room 5 - a standard studio!



