xinni_x



Singapore, Singapore





Level 3  Contributor 


12 reviews 


6 hotel reviews





3 helpful votes 





“Helpful hosts, lovely and comfortable room”


Reviewed March 13, 2012




We stayed in the deluxe studio, which was spacious, clean, and very well-equipped to ensure a comfortable stay. The welcome cookies and sweets were a nice touch too. Many thanks to Jeff who assisted us in so many ways. He kindly emailed us in advance to advise us on the congested roads to avoid, helped us book our dinner at Bodhi Tree, and told us about the places to explore in Christchurch. His willingness to go the extra mile left an impression with us. We would stay here again when we return to Christchurch.





Stayed March 2012, traveled as a couple



