“Must agree with other recent reviews!”


Reviewed March 12, 2012




This was our first stop in NZ, and what a great way to start. Helpful, informative owners, clean, spacious accommodations, and attention to detail. The other recent reviews of this property are right on. I hope to come back to Christchurch, and would definitely stay here again. My heart goes out to the people of Christchurch...still a wonderful city despite all the quake damage. Thanks for a wonderful stay!


