“Great spot in Christchurch”


Reviewed March 8, 2012




The Centerpoint on Columbo was the perfect place to stay to explore Christchurch on foot. Jeff pointed out must see places and helped with travel out to Akaroa. It was very clean and spacious and we would definately return. The small kitchen and refrigerator were a big plus as we had just moved out of a camper. Thanks Jeff!





