eurocarpaul



Los Angeles, California





Level 6  Contributor 


164 reviews 


62 hotel reviews





99 helpful votes 





“Great lodging, friendly and helpful owners.”


Reviewed March 6, 2012




The room itself was nice, and clean with a small kitchen and good sized bathroom. They have laundry facilities on-site, but be aware that there is only one washer and one dryer, so hopefully you won't be competing with anyone for their use (we had no issues doing our laundry at about 9 am). The owners are so friendly and helpful with places to eat, things to do, and navigating the city. I would recommend this as a place to stay.





Stayed February 2012, traveled as a couple



